                  <Label layoutX="14.0" layoutY="79.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="921.0" text="1. Binary Options Trading allows users to cash in a particular amount and predict whether the price level for a selected option will rise or " textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="14.0" layoutY="108.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="921.0" text="   fall after a selected period of time. Users can earn almost double the amount they invest or even lose all of it." textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="14.0" layoutY="142.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="940.0" text="2. CALL option is where users predict the price level for a selected currency to increase after a specified amount of time. If the user prediction" textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="14.0" layoutY="170.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="921.0" text="   turns out to be right, he/she is awarded the amount invested with an additional amount depending on the profit rate." textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="14.0" layoutY="203.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="937.0" text="3. PUT option is selected when the user feels that the price level for a selected currency will drop. The amount earned for the right prediction" textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="14.0" layoutY="231.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="921.0" text="   is same as in CALL in the call option." textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="14.0" layoutY="263.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="937.0" text="4. In case of a wrong prediction, the user loses all the invested amount. " textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="14.0" layoutY="293.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="937.0" text="5. To give users an added advantage on what choice to pick, the rising type icon (          ) is displayed on the choice (CALL or PUT)." textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="14.0" layoutY="321.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="921.0" text="   This lets the user know what the highest picked choice is for the selected currencies or binary option." textFill="WHITE" />
                  <ImageView fitHeight="21.0" fitWidth="20.0" layoutX="563.0" layoutY="293.0" pickOnBounds="true" preserveRatio="true">
