                     </image></ImageView>
                  <Label layoutX="14.0" layoutY="353.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="937.0" text="6. The user can also find a tip that analyzes the historical data and provides them with a suggestion on what option to put their money on." textFill="WHITE" />
