                  <Label layoutX="16.0" layoutY="462.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="921.0" text="1. Investments is more of a long term process when compared to Binary Option Trading. It allows users to invest on a specific " textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="16.0" layoutY="488.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="921.0" text="   cryptocurrency. When the user successfully invests on a currency, a gap is generated between which the user will not make any profits. " textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="16.0" layoutY="515.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="921.0" text="   If the price level goes above the gap/margin, user is allowed to take a profit. If the price level falls below the margin, the user is given an" textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="16.0" layoutY="541.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="921.0" text="   option to stop their losses so they do not incur any more losses in the future." textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="16.0" layoutY="572.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="921.0" text="2. It is to be kept in mind that, when the user invests on a currency, a given price is deducted as part of the commission fee." textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="16.0" layoutY="602.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="921.0" text="3. There is no given time limit or an ending period, since investments are long term, the user can choose to withdraw at any given point." textFill="WHITE" />
