                  <Label layoutX="40.0" layoutY="744.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="927.0" text="No, Arlkon is a simulation platform that allows users to learn more about how binary trading or investments work in the real world." textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="40.0" layoutY="770.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="927.0" text="Users cannot input any real currency or withdraw them." textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="21.0" layoutY="813.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="628.0" text="2) Why are the currency levels not fully accurate?" textFill="WHITE">
