                  <Label layoutX="40.0" layoutY="944.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="927.0" text="For a particular feature, the user can have at most one transaction. For example, a user can have one transaction in Binary Options Trading" textFill="WHITE" />
                  <Label layoutX="40.0" layoutY="970.0" prefHeight="21.0" prefWidth="927.0" text="and another in investments." textFill="WHITE" />
